title: >>> Dodgeball UHAUL
body_text:
It's been a strange week "moving" back and forth from one date to another.
DODGEBALL 23, originally scheduled to be played on Saturday, January 21st, was rescheduled three times within the last week. After much confusion, DODGEBALL 23 finally has a set date.
DODGEBALL 23 takes place on Friday, January 20th, 2006.
The normal start time is in effect as always: 7PM.
